Sentencas: A shielded slot was designed for use in a typical current collector/gas distributor fuel cell and was formed from a series of arches with heights suitable for providing sufficient quantities of fuel gases and reaction areas.
Titulo: Effect of a shielded slot on a planar solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The shielded slot was substituted in place of the interconnect and offered several advantages in terms of mechanical support and electrical contact.
Titulo: Effect of a shielded slot on a planar solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: A three-dimensional (3-D) electrochemical reaction model and a microelectrode model of the planar solid oxide fuel cells (SOFC) were used to predict the performances of the shielded slots in planar SOFCs.
Titulo: Effect of a shielded slot on a planar solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Prior to analyzing the complex arrangement of the shielded slot, a variety of interconnect arrangements were simulated to understand the relationship between the gas supply and the electrical contact arrangements.
Titulo: Effect of a shielded slot on a planar solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The reactivity properties were examined and the most effective arrangement of shielded slots was identified in an effort to design an optimal shielded slot.
Titulo: Effect of a shielded slot on a planar solid oxide fuel cell
